{"title":"守灵者","authors":["山鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"守灵者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我这个部长，就是一个守灵牌”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——章伯钧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不喜欢晴朗的白日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不喜爱儿童幸福的笑容；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外车辆的喧嚣令他烦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边轮船的呼唤令他伤心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一样他是虔诚地敬爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是资本主义黑色的幽灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残烛闪着暗淡的黄光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"檀香伴着木鱼单调的声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日夜守护着死者的灵位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾诉着他心头的哀痛与“不平”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且不断地哀啼着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“复活吧，我的主啊，阿门！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}